My build was: {{item:3512}} {{item:3742}} {{item:3040}} {{item:3047}} {{item:3116}} {{item:3151}} 

Another bitch I had about this game is that I killed Yasuo in lane at least 5 times and another 3-5 times throughout mid game. He ended up 13/21/18 by doing nothing other than following Nautilus around and mashing R. He couldn't land a Q to save his life, and he was obliterated in lane. But it doesn't matter when you can mash R and get fed for doing nothing.
